Package: LinearRegression
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive tools for Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yuka Kato, Lilian Yuan, Chloe Si
Description: This package provides tools for linear regression analysis, 
    including ordinary least squares (OLS) estimation, ridge regression, 
    confidence intervals and hypothesis testing for coefficients, 
    model comparison via AIC and BIC, ANOVA for categorical and continuous 
    predictors, and prediction with optional confidence intervals.
